name: Add update method

name: watchOS
body: Project cleanup, add a build server, and add a watchOS target.

name: Swift 2 & protocol oriented design
body:
Ground-up redesign of Locksmith to be protocol oriented, just in time for Swift 2!

This adds a huge amount of functionality, flexibility, and power, while still maintaining the key parts of the old, easy-to-use API.

- Minor fixes and improvements related to Swift
- Add Carthage support
- Drop iOS version requirement to 8.0
- Update tests
Version 1.2.1 which adds support for Swift 1.2
Adds support for default values for service name

name: Cocoapods
body: Adds support for installation via Cocoapods

body: This is the initial release for Locksmith.
